---
InheritParentConfig: true
# Disabled because the libc shims deliberately redeclare libc syscall wrappers as weak references when
# glibc's headers already declare them, so call sites can do runtime fallback. The corresponding
# -Wredundant-decls compiler warning is suppressed via c_args in src/libc/meson.build.
Checks: '-readability-redundant-declaration'
...
